snippet.textDisplay: It make me think about our invention before bitcoin was introduced, my team already working on ecoin. We try to invent an electronic coin that can be used securely and anonymously. it uses a "majority acknowledge acceptance (MAA)" system, and it works exactly like the "blockchain" but ugly. We decided to dump that project after we proved that the system is exploitable and some of other knowledge limitations. We also moving to college and the time and access to internet is very limited. Google and yahoo search is our teachers, mIRC script is our base knowledge and our first platform to script it. Our 1st and last beta version of ecoin has been released in the year of 2005 with a lot of bugs. That's how it ends and forgotten.
